Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:10.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(517,517)\blur2}前路未知　步履蹣跚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:14.75,OPCN,nofadeout,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(517,517)\blur2}眼前之物轉瞬整潔如初
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:19.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(517,517)\blur2}並非虛像　並非幻聽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:24.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(517,517)\blur2}聲樂輕撫　治癒我的傷口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:29.73,OPCN,nofadeout,0,0,0,fx,{\fad(517,517)\blur2}步入歧途只需笑著說大家都一樣
